OL,4,Ccutbacks will hit Manchester services
OL,6,FThat was echoed by a Manchester
OL,7,Fbusiness owner, who often travels to
OL,8,FLondon the night before a meeting, who
OL,9,Ftold MPs he "can't rely" on Avanti.
OL,11,FRail minister Huw Merriman said
OL,12,FAvanti's performance had "improved
OL,13,Fdramatically" when the Government last
OL,14,Fyear decided to renew its operating
OL,15,Fcontract for up to nine years.
