OL,3,CAvanti must 'do better' amid fears HS2
OL,4,Ccutbacks will hit Manchester services
OL,6,FIn response to Labour MP Jeff Smith
OL,7,F(Manchester Withington) asking if the
OL,8,FGovernment regretted the "premature
OL,9,Fdecision", Mr Merriman also told the
OL,10,FCommons: "Avanti are in the process of
OL,11,Fhiring 70 drivers per year.
OL,13,F"I have spoken to Avanti about matters
OL,14,Fthat were raised in the chamber today
OL,15,Fand also about their recent service,
OL,16,Fwe know they need to do better, we are
OL,17,Fholding them to account to ensure that
OL,18,Fthey do."
OL,20,FShadow transport secretary Louise
OL,21,FHaigh earlier said:
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@IO]rD@JOUuD@AOUzD@IO]
