OL,6,F"What does the Secretary of State
OL,7,Fthink it says about the performance
OL,8,Fstandards in the contracts he signed
OL,9,Fwith failing operators that senior
OL,10,Fexecutives at Avanti, whose
OL,11,Fcancellations now run at 17%, could
OL,12,Fboast about the free money that's too
OL,13,Fgood to be true from the taxpayer?"
OL,15,FTransport Secretary Mark Harper
OL,16,Freplied: "Avanti haven't got any money
OL,17,Funder the performance regime because
OL,18,Fthey haven't delivered appropriate
OL,19,Fenough quality, demonstrating we only
OL,20,Fpay for good performance.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@cO]xD@JOU
