OL,6,F"On the specific issue she raises, I
OL,7,Fand the rail minister have raised that
OL,8,Fwith Avanti, senior executives at
OL,9,FFirst have agreed with us that those
OL,10,Fcomments were appalling and they are
OL,11,Ftaking steps to deal with that issue
OL,12,Fwithin the company."
OL,14,FMs Haigh countered: "They were
OL,15,Fdisgraceful from Avanti, but the
OL,16,Fproblem goes to the contracts that he
OL,17,Fis signing with such failing
OL,18,Foperators."
OL,20,FAvanti last month apologised for the
OL,21,F"isolated" incident.
