OL,3,CAvanti must 'do better' amid fears HS2
OL,4,Ccutbacks will hit Manchester services
OL,6,FElsewhere at transport questions,
OL,7,Fshadow transport minister Stephen
OL,8,FMorgan said a leaked document shows
OL,9,Fthe decision to cut parts of HS2 will
OL,10,Freduce capacity on the West Coast Main
OL,11,FLine.
OL,13,FIn October last year, Prime Minister
OL,14,FRishi Sunak cancelled the plan to
OL,15,Fextend HS2 between the West Midlands
OL,16,Fand Manchester amid spiralling costs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
