OL,3,CAvanti must 'do better' amid fears HS2
OL,4,Ccutbacks will hit Manchester services
OL,6,FMr Morgan said: "When the Prime
OL,7,FMinister made the decision to scrap
OL,8,FHS2, his department said the plan
OL,9,Fwould 'lead to increased capacity on
OL,10,Fthe West Coast Main Line'. But,
OL,11,Fminister, that's not correct, is it?
OL,13,F"I have a leaked document from his own
OL,14,Fofficials that proves it. In it, they
OL,15,Fadmit that this decision will mean
OL,16,Ffewer seats than today, with Glasgow
OL,17,Fand Manchester badly hit ... does he
OL,18,Faccept he will be the high-speed rail
OL,19,Fminister who left behind slower trains
OL,20,Fand fewer seats?"
OL,26,@nD@QOUuD@AOU|D@QO]
