OL,3,CAvanti must 'do better' amid fears HS2
OL,4,Ccutbacks will hit Manchester services
OL,6,FMr Merriman said: "We don't comment on
OL,7,Fdocuments that may or may not have
OL,8,Fbeen leaked ... the HS2 train design
OL,9,Fwas always to have a capacity for 500
OL,10,Fseats.
OL,12,F"If those trains are doubled up to 400
OL,13,Fmetres, then, of course, that's 1,000
OL,14,Fseats. The Network North document
OL,15,Fcommitted half a billion pounds to
OL,16,Flook at capacity and how further
OL,17,Fcapacity can be unlocked."
