OL,6,FHe said the HS2 line "being built to
OL,7,FBirmingham" will "reduce the journey
OL,8,Ftimes to Birmingham" as well as to
OL,9,FManchester and Liverpool.
OL,11,FAn Avanti West Coast spokesman said in
OL,12,Fa statement: "We would like to
OL,13,Fapologise to our customers who had
OL,14,Ftheir journeys affected by previous
OL,15,Fcancellations on our network and thank
OL,16,Fthem for their patience.
OL,18,F"In December, we experienced a
OL,19,Fshortage of train crew due to historic
OL,20,Fleave agreements, elevated sickness
OL,21,Flevels and ongoing industrial disputes.
