OL,3,CAvanti must 'do better' amid fears HS2
OL,4,Ccutbacks will hit Manchester services
OL,6,F"As with all operators, we also
OL,7,Fexperienced issues during this period
OL,8,Fwith infrastructure and weather-
OL,9,Frelated challenges on the network,
OL,10,Fmeaning that we had to cancel an
OL,11,Fincreased number of services. This had
OL,12,Fa bearing on our previously improved
OL,13,Flevels of performance."
OL,15,FThe company expects timetable changes
OL,16,Fand driver recruitment and training to
OL,17,Fhelp in the long term, and
OL,18,Fcancellations for which it is
OL,19,Fresponsible have decreased to below 5%
OL,20,Fin the last four-week period.
